      "content": "i've been letting myself feel it, but there's no relief in this. it's just constant. every morning is just a fresh wave of realizing they aren't coming back. it feels like i'm just waiting for the pain to stop, but it never does. it's like i'm stuck in a room with no doors and the walls are just closing in. i just want the noise to stop. i just want to not feel this anymore. is there even any other way for this to end?",
